title: Antietam National Battlefield: Newpaper Sketches
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Photo Gallery     Newpaper Sketches                Historic Newspaper Sketches of Antietam Battlefield                    Historic Sketches   9 Photos  Alfred Waud, Edwin Forbes and Frank Schell were all artists that created many images of battle that appeared in publications like Frank Leslie's Illustrated Newspaper and Harpers Weekly.
